region		box block 0 ${nx} 0 ${ny} 0 ${nz} units lattice
region		box block 0 30 0 ${ny} 0 ${nz} units lattice
region		box block 0 30 0 5 0 ${nz} units lattice
region		box block 0 30 0 5 0 5 units lattice

